Name: Divine Creator (Marvel Comics)
Summary: In the J.M. DeMatteis version of the Marvel Comics cosmology, the Divine Creator is God hirself dreaming of all existence in the timeless sea of nothingness for aeons. A divine being that radiaities love at the core of Creation and every being in Creation connected to the infinity that sprung their essence from nothingness. A being that sits behind, beyond, and within all the hearts of hir creation and in the reality of illusions should one breakthrough, and strip their individual to merge back to Love, to Oneness itself again.
